(45, 'about.element', '{\"title\":\"Secured Services\",\"sub_title\":\"We offer a wide range of other courier services, such as same-day freight delivery, medical courier services, and rush package delivery. We trained our couriers to specialize in particular deliveries to meet the qualifications and standards of these industries because we are aware that businesses have a variety of delivery requirements.\\r\\nStork Track Couriers can provide you with any kind of urgent or same-day delivery that you require. Our trained delivery drivers and award-winning customer service make it simple to get your package to its destination and give you peace of mind that it will always arrive on time.\",\"about_icon\":\"<i class=\\\"lab la-delicious\\\"><\\/i>\"}', '2021-06-30 05:19:18', '2022-10-25 23:56:07'),
(47, 'about.element', '{\"title\":\"National Utility\",\"sub_title\":\"National rush deliveries are our specialty as a courier service. As a result, if you need a package delivered anywhere in the nation, we will do our best to do so as soon as possible. Stork Track Couriers ensures the safety of all of your important and fragile deliveries thanks to our GPS-equipped delivery drivers and bonding. Because we pick up your item at point A and drive it straight to point B, you don\'t have to worry about it breaking during shipping.\",\"about_icon\":\"<i class=\\\"lab la-servicestack\\\"><\\/i>\"}', '2021-06-30 05:20:25', '2022-10-25 23:56:42'),
