(71, 'faq.element', '{\"question\":\"How quickly can you deliver my package?\",\"answer\":\"Our rush courier and delivery services can vary in terms of delivery time. It also depend of the courier Service that you have selected. Our standard delivery time is between 3 to 5 days across any country\"}', '2021-06-30 08:16:38', '2022-10-25 23:46:06'),
(72, 'faq.element', '{\"question\":\"What does it cost for a courier?\",\"answer\":\"Prices for our courier and delivery services will vary depending on the item\'s size and weight, the kind of vehicle you need, the speed at which you need the item delivered, and the distance between your pick-up location and the delivery location.For a precise quote, get in touch with us or fill out our online request form.\"}', '2021-06-30 08:17:10', '2022-10-25 23:46:39'),
