(94, 'footer.element', '{\"menu\":\"Privacy and Policy\",\"description\":\"<div class=\\\"mb-5\\\" style=\\\"color:rgb(111,111,111);font-family:Nunito, sans-serif;margin-bottom:3rem;\\\"><h3 class=\\\"mb-3\\\" style=\\\"font-weight:600;line-height:1.3;font-size:24px;font-family:Exo, sans-serif;color:rgb(54,54,54);\\\"><\\/h3><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin:15pt 0in 7.5pt;line-height:normal;background-size:initial;\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size:24pt;font-family:Arial, \'sans-serif\';color:#0070C0;text-transform:uppercase;\\\">STORK TRACK PRIVACY\\r\\nPOLICY<\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p><b><\\/b><\\/p><b><\\/b><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:7.5pt;line-height:normal;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial, \'sans-serif\';color:#6F7174;\\\">Last Updated on10\\/01\\/2022.\\r\\nThis privacy policy is effective immediately.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin:15pt 0in 7.5pt;line-height:normal;background-size:initial;\\\"><b><span style=\\\"font-size:18pt;font-family:Arial, \'sans-serif\';color:#0070C0;text-transform:uppercase;\\\">INTRODUCTION<\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p><b><\\/b><\\/p><b><\\/b><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:7.5pt;line-height:normal;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial, \'sans-serif\';color:#6F7174;\\\">At Stork Track (the\\r\\n\\u201cCompany\\u201d or\\u00a0\\u201cWe\\u201d), we respect your privacy and are committed to\\r\\nprotecting it through our compliance with this policy.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:7.5pt;line-height:normal;background-size:initial;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial, \'sans-serif\';color:#6F7174;\\\">This policy describes\\r\\nthe types of information we may collect from you or that you may provide when\\r\\nyou visit this website (our \\u201cWebsite\\u201d) and our practices for collecting, using,\\r\\nmaintain